  "detailed_description": "<strong>Boss Of This Gym</strong> is a unique runner expirences, which will fullfill your ♂<strong>deep dark fantasies</strong>♂ of dominating <u>Van</u> and his ♂<strong>Slaves</strong>♂<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1396890/extras/9114f1ecbd8fee500579ce0c43be964a.avif?t=1655415126\" width=640 height=360 /></span><br><br>You start as a <strong>weakling</strong>, with a cheap <strong>car</strong> and no <strong>drinks</strong> to <u>help</u> you. Collect weights to exchange them for some <strong>tonics</strong> and a new <strong>ride</strong>. Upgrade yourself by <u>buying</u> <strong>masks</strong> which will increase the amount of weights you gain.<br><br><strong><u><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unique characteristics</h2></u></strong><br>-Lots of obstacles and things not ot ♂<strong>stick your finger</strong>♂ into <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1396890/extras/376190366f67da91d6fa618786084054.webp?t=1655415126\" width=18 height=28 /></span><br>-Different <strong>masks</strong> and various upgrades for your <strong>racing machine</strong> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1396890/extras/e017031ea86ff4ff0eab5a8fe4e154e4.webp?t=1655415126\" width=30 height=29 /></span><br>-<strong>Tonics</strong> will help you if you fall <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1396890/extras/bc77163d6c7b26a073ab3aea07022550.webp?t=1655415126\" width=30 height=27 /></span> <br>-<u><strong>UNIQUE</strong></u> boss fight <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1396890/extras/32ffd1f84a1de3495c24640f6dcec2fa.webp?t=1655415126\" width